‚ö†Ô∏è Risks & Trade-Offs
Too heavy boots ‚Üí cause fatigue when standing long hours.

Poor arch support ‚Üí leads to back pain and plantar fasciitis.

Non-waterproof designs ‚Üí sand mixed with moisture can seep in, causing cold feet.

Fashion boots ‚Üí may lack durability for sandy terrain.

‚úÖ Expert Tips
Add gel insoles or orthotic inserts for extra cushioning.

Rotate footwear to prevent wear and odor buildup.

Pair with moisture-wicking socks to keep feet warm and dry.

Choose mid-calf or tall boots if sand depth is significant.
